</td>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-even">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em"><a href="/wiki/Insomnia" title="Insomnia">Insomnia</a> <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Hypersomnia" title="Hypersomnia">Hypersomnia</a> <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Sleep_apnea" title="Sleep apnea">Sleep apnea</a> (<a href="/wiki/Obstructive_sleep_apnea" title="Obstructive sleep apnea">Obstructive</a>, <a href="/wiki/Ondine%27s_curse" title="Ondine's curse">Ondine's curse</a>) <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Narcolepsy" title="Narcolepsy">Narcolepsy</a> <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Cataplexy" title="Cataplexy">Cataplexy</a> <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Kleine-Levin_syndrome" title="Kleine-Levin syndrome">Kleine-Levin</a> <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Circadian_rhythm_sleep_disorder" title="Circadian rhythm sleep disorder">Circadian rhythm sleep</a> <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Delayed_sleep_phase_syndrome" title="Delayed sleep phase syndrome">Delayed sleep phase</a> <span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Advanced_sleep_phase_syndrome" title="Advanced sleep phase syndrome">Advanced sleep phase</a></div>
</td>
